《'''我的聾人朋友'''》一書收錄了八位不同年齡及背景的[[聾|聾]]人和[[弱聽|弱聽]]人士，講述他們的故事。

==成書背景==
此書的文字作者陳意軒<ref>{{Cite news |language=zh-hk |url=http://www.hket.com/eti/article/70f51121-86e3-4d56-a079-826a5455cb44-901887?section=012 |title=聾人朋友為手語抗爭 |publisher=[[香港經濟日報|經濟日報]] |date=2013-09-02 |accessdate=2013-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004212737/http://www.hket.com/eti/article/70f51121-86e3-4d56-a079-826a5455cb44-901887?section=012 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，與兩位聾人分別為路駿怡及沈栢基<ref>{{Cite news |language=zh-hk |url=http://programme.rthk.hk/channel/radio/programme.php?d=2013-10-05&p=421&e=&m=episode |title=開卷樂︰談《我的聾人朋友》 |publisher=[[香港電台|香港電台]] |date=2013-10-05 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2015-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610194729/http://programme.rthk.hk/channel/radio/programme.php?d=2013-10-05&p=421&e=&m=episode |dead-url=no }}</ref>，訪問了八位年齡及背景各異的聾人和弱聽人士，目的是要記錄他們的故事<ref>{{Cite news |language=zh-hk |url=http://www.hket.com/eti/article/d7b8e1f5-df8d-41f7-aa21-e2b5633ad2c4-901946?section=012 |title=本港手語和口語教學發展概況 |publisher=[[香港經濟日報|經濟日報]] |date=2013-09-02 |accessdate=2013-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004212838/http://www.hket.com/eti/article/d7b8e1f5-df8d-41f7-aa21-e2b5633ad2c4-901946?section=012 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|language=zh-hk|url=http://news.sina.com.hk/news/20131003/-23-3081195/1.html|title=聾人有話兒|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|date=2013-10-03|accessdate=2013-10-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213626/http://news.sina.com.hk/news/20131003/-23-3081195/1.html|archivedate=2013-10-04}}</ref>。當中，包括在日佔時期見證哥哥被斬頭、為救父母而拚命叩頭向日軍求饒的婆婆；有從小堅持刻苦訓練而能發音精準、聆聽不到琴聲但懂彈鋼琴，卻不擅交際的弱聽女子；不堪積壓已久的壓力而自殺的「聾人女狀元」；偷渡來港、到日本工作再回港創業的「手語講古佬」等<ref>{{Cite news |language=zh-hk |url=http://www2.mingpaoweekly.com/contents/?id=30451 |title=Bookeeper：《我的聾人朋友》 |publisher=[[明報周刊|明報周刊]] |date= |accessdate=2013-08-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004215712/http://www2.mingpaoweekly.com/contents/?id=30451 |archivedate=2013-10-04 }}</ref>。

==出版資訊==

出版社為圓桌精英，隨書附送本書的手語光碟，讓更多聾人能掌握書本各章節內容<ref>{{Cite news|language=zh-hk|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130710/18328935|title=佔中議題新書開賣|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報 (香港)]]|date=2013-07-10|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826185445/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130710/18328935|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |language=zh-hk |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130720/18341470 |title=夜市旺場　越多人越大鑊　網絡塞車　書商鬧爆貿發局 |publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報 (香港)]] |date=2013-07-20 |accessdate=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2017-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824231814/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130720/18341470 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

